# Regions Database
Our regions database focuses on cataloging online news by region. We have made it open-source so users can see our catalog and use it as a reference. Our [database](https://curatednews.xyz/static/downloads/CuratedRegionsDatabase.zip) is open-source and freely available.

Check out our [interactive search page/demo](https://curatednews.github.io/regionsdatabase/) and/or [codebook](https://curatednews.github.io/regionsdatabase/CuratedNewsRegionsCodeBook.pdf)

## Usage

Our JSON databases in JavaScript format are available for testing purposes only: 
[https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CuratedNews/regionsdatabase/main/regions/*country*/*region*.js](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CuratedNews/regionsdatabase/main/regions/united_states/curatedregionsalabama.js)

Where **country** is lowercase country name and **region** is lowercase region name. Use **_** instead of spaces where required.

## Data format example

### state/region
```
{"State":"Telangana",
```

### name of news source
```
"Name":"Telangana Today",
```

### link, title, substitle, & description of news site
```
"Link":"https:\/\/telanganatoday.com\/",
"Title":"Telangana Today - Latest Telangana News Headlines",
"Subtitle":null,
"Description":"Telangana Today brings the latest telangana news headlines, Telugu news & Hyderabad news, telangana politics and Live Updates on telangana & hyderabad.",
"Summary":null,
``` 

### RSS link (if available)
```
"RSS":"http:\/\/telanganatoday.com\/feed\/",
```

### image & image string logo
```
"Image":"https:\/\/cdn.telanganatoday.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Telangana-Today-News-1.jpg","ImageString":""
}
```

### complete example (minified)
```
{"State":"Telangana","Name":"Telangana Today","Link":"https:\/\/telanganatoday.com\/","Title":"Telangana Today - Latest Telangana News Headlines","Subtitle":null,"Description":"Telangana Today brings the latest telangana news headlines, Telugu news & Hyderabad news, telangana politics and Live Updates on telangana & hyderabad.","Summary":null,"RSS":"http:\/\/telanganatoday.com\/feed\/","Image":"https:\/\/cdn.telanganatoday.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Telangana-Today-News-1.jpg","ImageString":""}
```
